dev.jeka.core.api.crypto.gpg

Class JkGpg

  • java.lang.Object
    • dev.jeka.core.api.crypto.gpg.JkGpg

  • public final class JkGpg
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides method for signing and verify signature with PGP.

    When constructing JkGpg, you can provide a secret key ring, a public key ring or both.
